default2.3
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultRMT
default is concerned at the variation i
defaultn practice that exists amongst he
defaultlicopter companies operating in the North Sea
default and the potential consequences of this in terms of the safety of offshore oil and gas workers
default. For example, Bristow Helicopters operate to a "gold standard"
default,
default essentially the set of standards applied in the Norwegian sector 
defaultwhich are widely acknowledged
default as more robust than those in place for the UK sector. 
