defaultSuper Puma models AS332 L, L1, L2 and EC225 account for 60% of the helicopter fleet currently transporting the vast m
defaultajority of the 30,000 strong workforce employed in the UK offshore oil and gas industry. That is 45 out of a fleet of 75
default which has clocked up millions of flight hours and passengers 
defaultover the last ten years alone
